Class TransformExprToSQLApplyer

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fuberlin.wiwiss.d2rq.optimizer.expr.TransformExprToSQLApplyer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExprVisitor

    public final class TransformExprToSQLApplyer
extends Object
implements ExprVisitor
    Attempts to transform a SPARQL FILTER Expr to a SQL Expression Notes:
    • Literals using d2rq:pattern cannot be compared.
    • No XSD type checking/conversion or constructor functions yet.
    Author:
    Herwig Leimer, Giovanni Mels
